data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER.. Many updates in this beautiful home! You'll love the custom features such as walls w/ board & batten in the entry way, custom lighting, fresh paint and wallpaper, and complete Smart home monitored by ADT. Full Roof replacement in 2023, plus gutters all around and fresh landscaping. This popular Cali model has an open floor plan & 4 spacious bedrooms. The kitchen has lots of cabinetry & an island that can seat 4, dining area & spacious pantry. The split floor plan is by far the favorite having the primary bedroom located in the back of the home. It overlooks the large back yard, and has double sinks in the bathroom, soaker tub, walk-in shower & huge walk-in closet. Outside features a covered patio, or sit back and relax around the firepit with friends in the privacy of your fully fenced back yard. The Community offers a resort style pool, pavilion area w/gas grills, hot tub & playground.The neighborhood is centrally located in a very quiet part of Bay County, yet convenient to schools, shopping, Tyndall AFB, the Airport and the Beaches. Don't wait, schedule your showing today.  Ask about the Assumable VA loan for Qualified Buyers!
